(7472, 1979, 881, 6, 'Aspects Of Reality', '[馬來西亞]的吉他手兼創作歌手Sudev(蘇德夫)很早就投入「cc授權運動」，曾受邀來台參與「亞洲cc大車拼」音樂會，是為本「cc亞洲樂團」之雛形。此次，積極參與本CABACA，幾乎將每一首都加入他的電吉他。這首Aspects Of Reality為Sudev(蘇德夫)的原創，搖滾主耶穌的鼓手Bobo加上真打軍，MoShang稍微編理了一下，最後，朱約信模仿台灣原住民唱了幾句呼喚祖靈來跟電吉他的旋律相對應。', '2008-08-11 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, '', '', 209, 'Sudev Bangah', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2008-08-11 12:47:31', '2015-03-12 13:34:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7473, 1979, 881, 7, 'Moved By An Angel', 'Lisa diy是菲律賓知名流行歌曲作者，同時也是律師/法官，於2008年1月，受邀來台參與「ACIA」研討會，在「亞洲cc大車拼」音樂會演唱。首先，Lisa將這首Moved By An Angel丟給我們，馬來西亞的Sudev加上了電吉他，香港的Snoblind加上一些電子音效，Moshang再疊上更重的鼓，編曲重新混音。弄完之後，Lisa聽完興奮不已：「我從沒想到我的音樂熱情能讓我走這麼遠，跟這一群優秀音樂家的合作，簡直美夢成真!您們真是我的天使，撼動我的宇宙。」', '2008-08-11 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, '1. All my life I’ve had a shield\r\nAn armor to protect my heart\r\nThen one day I found my shield melting\r\nMelting away with my tears.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nChorus:\r\nI was moved by an angel\r\nTouched my life with his gentle/magical fingers\r\nOpened my heart, healed my wounds\r\nCalmed my mind.\r\nI was moved by an angel,\r\nMoved by an angel.\r\n\r\n\r\n2. All my life I’ve had a fortress\r\nA fortress made of stone and steel\r\nI was afraid of pain, afraid to feel\r\nThen he reached for my hand.\r\n\r\n\r\n(Repeat Chorus)\r\n(Interlude: Repeat 2nd to 4th lines of Chorus)\r\n(Repeat Chorus)\r\n\r\nCoda:\r\n\r\nMoved by an angel', '', 209, 'Lisa Diy', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2008-08-11 12:48:04', '2015-03-12 13:34:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7474, 1979, 881, 8, 'Crossing The Pond', 'Snoblind是香港的電音二人組，曾數次來台演唱；Anji Bee是美國知名另類魅惑電音二人組Lovespirals的創作主力兼主唱，早就常常支援美國cc活動，先前在網路上遇到本CABACA製作中心Moshang而結為知己，此次知道我們在弄這個「CC協力創作專輯」而大力投入。此曲Crossing The Pond是Snoblind先放到cabaca工作網上，Sudev加上吉他，Anji Bee加上旋律歌詞，唱著佛的道理，人生思考，慾望憎恨，思緒虛無，智慧光芒，奉獻圓滿…最後加上台灣朋友熟悉的「南無阿彌陀佛」，神遊之際突至虔誠廟堂。', '2008-08-11 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, 'Know ye not that this life is deceit?\r\nKnow ye not that enjoyment is illusion?\r\nKnow ye not the world is a passing show?\r\nKnow ye not that happiness is a dream?\r\nKnow ye not that praise and blame is insubstantial?\r\nKnow yet not that appearance is the mind itself?\r\n\r\nKnow yet not that the mind itself is Buddhahood?\r\nKnow yet not that the Buddhahood is the body of truth?\r\n\r\nWhen ye reflect, all appearances are compacted out of mind\r\nContemplate the mind by day and night\r\nFrom contemplation of the mind comes beatific vision\r\nAbide in that beatitude\r\n\r\nKnow ye not that the body of truth is truth itself? (x2)\r\n\r\nWhen ye meditate upon these things\r\nThough ye do not succeed in rooting out desire and hatred\r\nKnow that whatever appears is your own mind-stuff\r\nAnd that the mind itself is void\r\nIf ye dwell in wisdom inseparably\r\nAll the observances of the law, oblations, and the like\r\nAre thus perfectly fulfilled', '', 259, 'Snoblind, Anji Bee', 'Snoblind', 'Anji Bee', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2008-08-11 12:57:16', '2015-03-12 13:34:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7475, 1979, 881, 9, 'Favor Tweet', '此曲是透過日本cc介紹，從一張日本出版的cc授權合輯上選錄，台灣鼓手波波加上鼓，美國的anji bee唱了＆念了一些東西上去，莫尚將之完成。非常優美的背景，熱愛東方文化的美國人anji bee唱了日語進去，甚是有趣。', '2008-08-11 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, 'watashi no\r\naware na\r\nkokoro ga\r\nitandeiru\r\n\r\nmy poor heart oh how it is aching\r\ncan you hear the sound of it breaking\r\nshow pity on the one you''re forsaking\r\nlook at all the love here for the taking\r\n\r\nwatashi no\r\naware na\r\nkokoro ga\r\nitandeiru', '', 224, 'イシカワ.タケル', '石川 長', 'Anji Bee', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2008-08-11 12:57:53', '2015-03-12 13:34:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7476, 1979, 881, 10, 'Free Music 2', 'Cho PD.是韓國的知名dj嘻哈rapper, 此曲本為Cho PD.受韓國cc之邀為推廣cc而作, 苦口婆心而輕鬆地以英文/韓文述說著cc的樂趣：「歡迎來到新世界，共同創造，愛音樂的人善變，消費者渴望著被刺激，音樂的世界不斷創新，打開自己，勇敢接受…新的世界來臨，快跟上，重新與創造連接，天空是我們的界限，新的遠景所有未來的音樂和電影創作，這太屌了寶貝，打開你的心這是全新的日子…」。此次我們邀請此曲, 並加上Moshang的電音薩克斯風。', '2008-08-11 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, 'welcome to the new world \r\nwelcome to the new world, creative commons\r\nwelcome to the new world, song, picture, video and so on\r\nwelcome to the new world, creative commons\r\n\r\nLook, 기억할 수 있을 만큼 어릴 적\r\n항상 음악에 미쳐 잠겨있던 기억\r\n이제 뮤지션 명함은 없어도 되는 직업\r\n세월 앞엔 장사 없는 법\r\n\r\n때 묻지 않은 그때\r\n카세트 늘어나게 듣네\r\n매일 음반가게 들러 새로 나온 음반 있나 물었네\r\n\r\n2천하고 몇 년도 강산은 몇 번을 변했고\r\n지나간 시절의 이전의 전설은\r\n상상도 못할 새로운 시대가 왔고\r\n\r\n팬은 죽고 소비자만 남고\r\n음악의 의미도 이전 같지 않아 no more\r\nfree your mind\r\nopen up\r\nit''s a brand new days, come on\r\n\r\nwelcome to the new world, creative commons\r\nsong, picture, video and so on\r\nshare, remix, reuse\r\nit''s a new world of creative commons\r\n\r\nwelcome to the new world, creative commons\r\nsong, picture, video and so on\r\nshare, remix, reuse\r\nit''s a new world of creative commons\r\n\r\ndo you really love music man\r\n어린 내 귀엔 늘 워크맨 꽂고\r\n자라나면서 몇 개의 밴드 거쳐\r\n뮤지션으로 자란 난데\r\n\r\nI pronounce now that the music is dead\r\npeople are people they going deaf\r\nI heard that too\r\nI hear Nas said\r\nhiphop is dead but I think music is dead\r\n\r\nnow, 크리에이티비티를 되살려\r\nsky is the limit \r\n봐 예를 들어 Bass in Korea, guitar in America, Mix by whomever, whenever\r\nit''s a vision of music and movie may be\r\nisn''t it great baby\r\n\r\n세계 어디 누구나 날 대신해서 할 수 있게\r\nit''s so cool and international\r\n\r\nwelcome to the new world, creative commons\r\nsong, picture, video and so on\r\nshare, remix, reuse\r\nit''s a new world of creative commons\r\n\r\nwelcome to the new world, creative commons\r\nsong, picture, video and so on\r\nshare, remix, reuse\r\nit''s a new world of creative commons\r\n\r\nremix this that''s okay\r\nyou can do anything with it\r\ncuz that''s just what I said\r\nfree your mind it''s a brand new days\r\n\r\nremix this go ahead\r\nyou can do anything with it\r\ncuz that''s just what I said\r\nfree your mind it''s a brand new days, come on', '', 208, 'Cho PD.', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2008-08-11 12:58:25', '2015-03-12 13:34:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7477, 1979, 881, 11, 'Turntable Sound', 'DJ Jangga.是[韓國嘻哈團體]「bust this」一員, 曾發行過cc授權專輯。並受邀於2008年1月，來台參與「ACIA」研討會，在「亞洲cc大車拼」音樂會表演演唱。我們收到這首歌時，突發奇想…原本香港snoblind作給Cho PD.一段電子音效但趕不上最後混音期限，我們就將之移來這首歌，效果也不錯。最後，莫尚再將之整理一下。', '2008-08-11 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, '', '', 147, 'DJ Jangga', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2008-08-11 12:58:55', '2015-03-12 13:34:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
